\par\pard\plain \tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\sl264\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs26\b0\i0\cf1 The Agency\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s understanding of time would be considerably different from inside the Enclosure.  That is where sci-fi / space fiction considerations need to come into play, especially regarding relativity, near-light-speed travel and/or traveling vast distances thru space. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs26\b0\i0\cf1 But don\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92t get TOO carried away with complex physics; it\u8217\'92s not really the realm of this story and the intention is for the Agency to be \u8220\'93not all there\u8221\'94 any way.}
